Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//正文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我逃了  腳完全動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去就會毫不客氣地來纏著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被砍人魔襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想加入DOLLARS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正臣你是沒法逃離過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
